        | An Audio Player in Java, built in Android Studio, uses the MediaPlayer class for audio playback. It
        | allows users to play, pause, and stop audio files.
      .btns
        a.label(href='#none' onclick="alert('No Path Defined');") Code Here
        a.label(href='#none' onclick="alert('App Not Uploaded On PlayStore Yet');") Download Apk
    .card
